title: FP91G
author: FP91G
content: Please don't do this - AliExpress GPU Backplate Coolinghttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VZayTZg3ajU&ab_channel=der8auerENThere are many opinions on this topic, but I heard positive reviews about such devices for hot 3080 and 3090 video cards, and it helped to reduce memory temperatures.It makes no sense to install such a device on budget graphics cards.
